%% ML Metadata (MLMD) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4/ml-metadata.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP Pipeline Controller<br/>gRPC Client
    participant DSPUI as DSP UI / Pipeline Client<br/>gRPC Client
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS + mTLS
    participant DB as MySQL/MariaDB or PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP or 5432/TCP<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution / PutArtifacts / PutEvents<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (Optional TLS)<br/>Optional mTLS Auth
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL wire protocol<br/>Optional TLS, Username/Password Auth
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Query Result
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>DSP: gRPC Response (status, IDs)
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Metadata Retrieval / Lineage Query

    DSPUI->>MLMD: GetArtifacts / GetExecutions / GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (Optional TLS)<br/>Optional mTLS Auth
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT metadata records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL wire protocol<br/>Optional TLS, Username/Password Auth
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Result Set (artifacts, executions, contexts)
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>DSPUI: gRPC Response (metadata objects, lineage graph)
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 3: Type Registration (Setup)

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifactType / PutExecutionType / PutContextType<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE type definitions<br/>Schema migration if enabled
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Type IDs
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>DSP: gRPC Response (type IDs)
    deactivate MLMD
